    "notes": "Used by many BCBS plans (IL, TX, CA, VA, AL, MA, NV, Premera, Regence, Independence, Highmark) and Anthem Medicaid (criteria only, submit via Availity). Symptoms-first model similar to Evicore. Updated: keyword arrays for OCR matching.",
